OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with any early morning
OL,6,Fcloud soon burning off to leave a very
OL,7,Fwarm day with sunny spells. Fresher
OL,8,Faround some coasts with sea breezes
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine end to the day and
OL,12,Fstaying dry overnight. Low cloud and
OL,13,FHaar could develop around the Angus
OL,14,Fcoast overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright and
OL,17,Fvery warm inland. Low cloud and Haar
OL,18,Fcould affect some North Sea coasts and
OL,19,Fheavy showers perhaps breaking out
OL,20,Flater in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
